      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "The Hot and Cold Treatment",
        "Client": "Knackered Felyne",
        "Description": "Hasn\u0027t the tem-purr-ature in\r\nthe Citadel been all over the\r\nplace lately? Ice chunks and\r\nflaming pinecones flying all\r\nover... My cargo\u0027s done fur at\r\nthis rate. Do something about\r\nthe purr-rojectiles at least!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Goss Harag and\r\na Blood Orange Bishaten",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Chaud et froid",
        "Client": "Felyne harass\u00E9",
        "Description": "Qu\u0027est-ce qui se passe avec\r\nla temp\u00E9rature \u00E0 la Citadelle ?\r\nOn passe d\u0027un extr\u00EAme \u00E0 l\u0027autre\r\nen permanence... C\u0027est pas\r\nbon pour mes marchandises,\r\n\u00E7a. Si tu pouvais t\u0027occuper\r\ndes pommes de pin au moins...",
        "Target": "Chasser un Goss Harag\r\net un Bishaten sanguin",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Sbalzo termico",
        "Client": "Felyne distrutta",
        "Description": "La temperatura alla cittadella\r\n\u00E8 impazzita, non trovi? Volano\r\npezzi di ghiaccio e pigne di\r\nfuoco... Di questo passo, il\r\nmio carico pu\u00F2 considerarsi\r\nperso. Fai qualcosa, almeno\r\nper fermare i proiettili, miao!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Goss Harag\r\ne un Bishaten sanguigno",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Feuer und Eis",
        "Client": "Todm\u00FCde Felyne",
        "Description": "Ist die Temperatur in der Zita-\r\ndelle in letzter Zeit nicht au\u00DFer\r\nRand und Band? Eisbrocken\r\nund Tannenzapfen fliegen \u00FCberall\r\nherum... Wenn das so weiter-\r\ngeht, ist es aus mit meiner Ware.\r\nTu was gegen die Projektile!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Goss Harag\r\nund einen Blut-Bishaten.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Tratamiento de calor y fr\u00EDo",
        "Client": "Felyne exhausto",
        "Description": "\u00BFNo cambia la temperatura del\r\nBasti\u00F3n mucho \u00FAltimamente? Hay\r\ntrozos de hielo y pi\u00F1as en\r\nllamas por doquier. A este\r\npaso, me quedo sin mercanc\u00EDas.\r\n\u00A1Arregla al menos lo de esos\r\nproyectiles, miau!",
